item.title: Filemanager help
item.dc:creator: @Team_Rocket Team_Rocket
item.description:
@Team_Rocket wrote:

[quote=“Jazzelhawk, post:1, topic:426538”]What do the different numbers after the line.substring stand for?

else if (line.startsWith("starter:")) p.starter = Integer.parseInt(line.substring(8)); else if (line.startsWith("jailed:")) p.jailed = Integer.parseInt(line.substring(7)); else if (line.startsWith("KC: ")) p.KC = Integer.parseInt(line.substring(4));[/quote]

The space allotted for the string. The longer the word, the higher the number.
